	<string>Universal Converter for Alfred

Keywords: c, ct

Convert (c):
  c 12pm to pdt
  c 3:30pm kst to est
  c 1000 krw to usd
  c 50 eur to jpy

Timezone Dashboard (ct):
  ct              — show current time in saved timezones
  ct 10am         — show 10am converted to saved timezones
  ct add tokyo    — add a timezone
  ct remove tokyo — remove a timezone

Press Enter to copy result or add/remove timezone.</string>
